game.name: Knives Extreme
game.description:
Action-packed challenges are the best thing to try especially when you seek for the mind-boggling thrill and long engaging hours. Today we have got you covered with a brand new fast-paced action challenge where the gameplay is all about throwing knives at the moving wood. Is not pretty exciting and challenging? If yes, join Knives Extreme, grab your knives and gear up to show off the world that you are equipped with matchless expertise in hitting the targets. 

Hitting knives perfectly will help to reward you with some points. Remember the wood surface will keep rotating all the time. Do not get your knives overlapped with the other one otherwise, you will lose the game immediately. Be careful and also try to hit the apples available on the wood while avoiding the previous knives in this HTML5 shooting game! All you need to put your shooting and concentration skills to the test to hit the knives on the moving wood for long. 

Practice wisely to launch all your knives on the wood to gain a high score in each level! Do not bother at all since you will have plenty of levels to try out during your vacant hours. Good luck to target nicely to complete your all levels and set your new best score! If this action-packed shooter challenge has given you some good fun moments, do not hesitate in browsing through our wider array of free action games to keep you busy for long.
